snippet.title: PAW Patrol Pups vs. Mayor Humdinger! | 30 Minute Compilation | Nick Jr.
snippet.description:
Mayor Humdinger is never up to any good! Check out this 30 minute compilation filled with every time the PAW Patrol pups stopped one of Mayor Humdinger's evil plans!
